Bio-Digital Twin platform (v\VAR{software_version}, commit
\texttt{\VAR{git_commit}})~\cite{cognisom2026}. The platform integrates
nine simulation modules: cellular dynamics, immune surveillance,
vascular oxygen delivery, lymphatic transport, molecular signaling,
spatial diffusion, epigenetic regulation, circadian gating, and
morphogen gradient computation.

